> **Note:** All endpoints require a valid JWT token from Keycloak. Use the curl command below to obtain a token.

### Create reminder
POST /api/v1/reminder/create
Request body:
```json
{
  "title": "Test reminder",
  "description": "Description",
  "remind": "2026-02-27T10:00:00"
}
